始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"fd9c83603bfc598500c93b08994b74b6f01ac7c9","tid":2298094,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都已經凍到射精"},{"pid":"89bc6f214d26b880aec56026f3d098da4306c4d4","tid":2298094,"uid":6290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T01:39:54.000Z","msg":"到今日都係開緊冷氣瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db3d2342988919661b74951e7275f06e728c667","tid":2298094,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T01:44:13.000Z","msg":"邊撚到凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}